7 expert.
8 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Legislature of Louisiana does hereby
9 commend Angela Lasyone for her contributions to the Natchitoches Parish showcase on the
10 occasion of Natchitoches Day at the state capitol and does hereby extend sincere wishes that
11 she remain prosperous in all of her endeavors, especially those that celebrate Louisiana's
12 vibrant food culture.
